{"page_id": 8581, "slug": "Groundwork_of_Evangelion", "title": "Groundwork of Evangelion", "display_title": "<span class=\"mw-page-title-main\">Groundwork of Evangelion</span>", "namespace": 0, "content_model": "wikitext", "language": null, "wikitext": "[[Image:MassProductionEvaDamage.gif|thumb|right|An image from Groundwork of Evangelion the Movie #2]]\nThe '''Groundwork of Evangelion''' is a collection of 5 artbooks which contain a large number of production sketches and a few colored plates in the beginning of each one. The first covers episodes 1 through 8, the second covers episodes 9 through 19, and the third covers episodes 20 through 26. The last 2 books are called ''Groundwork of Evangelion the Movie'' #1 and #2, the first covering [[Death]] and [[Episode 25']] and the second covering [[Episode 26']].\n\n{{Template:Stub}}\n\n{{Pub List}}\n\n[[Category:A to Z]]\n[[Category:Publications]]", "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><figure class=\"mw-default-size mw-halign-right\" typeof=\"mw:File/Thumb\"><a href=\"/File:MassProductionEvaDamage.gif\" class=\"mw-file-description\"><img src=\"/images/thumb/3/31/MassProductionEvaDamage.gif/300px-MassProductionEvaDamage.gif\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"300\" height=\"257\" class=\"mw-file-element\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/3/31/MassProductionEvaDamage.gif/450px-MassProductionEvaDamage.gif 1.5x, /images/thumb/3/31/MassProductionEvaDamage.gif/600px-MassProductionEvaDamage.gif 2x\" /></a><figcaption>An image from Groundwork of Evangelion the Movie #2</figcaption></figure>\n<p>The <b>Groundwork of Evangelion</b> is a collection of 5 artbooks which contain a large number of production sketches and a few colored plates in the beginning of each one. The first covers episodes 1 through 8, the second covers episodes 9 through 19, and the third covers episodes 20 through 26. The last 2 books are called <i>Groundwork of Evangelion the Movie</i> #1 and #2, the first covering <a href=\"/Death\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Death\">Death</a> and <a href=\"/Episode_25%27\" title=\"Episode 25&#39;\">Episode 25'</a> and the second covering <a href=\"/Episode_26%27\" title=\"Episode 26&#39;\">Episode 26'</a>.\n</p><p><br clear=\"all\" />\n<i>This article bears the unpleasant designation of \"<b>Stub</b>.\" This is a <b>Bad Thing</b>. Provide a great service to NGE fan-geeks everywhere by <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://wiki.evageeks.org/index.php?title=Groundwork_of_Evangelion&amp;action=edit\">making it awesomer!</a></i>\n<br clear=\"all\" />\n</p><p><br />\n</p>\n<table class=\"infobox centered\" style=\"width: 60%; font-size: 90%; text-align: center; margin: 0 auto; clear: both; border: 1\" align=\"center\">\n\n<tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"background: DarkSeaGreen; font-size: 110%;\"><i><b>List of Official Publications</b></i>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><b>General</b>:  <a href=\"/Neon_Genesis_Evangelion_Newtype_Film_Books\" title=\"Neon Genesis Evangelion Newtype Film Books\">Newtype Film Books</a> | <a href=\"/Neon_Genesis_Evangelion_Newtype_100%25_Collection\" title=\"Neon Genesis Evangelion Newtype 100% Collection\">Newtype 100% Collection</a> | <a href=\"/Movie_Pamphlets\" title=\"Movie Pamphlets\">Movie Pamphlets</a> | <a href=\"/Eva_Fan_Club\" title=\"Eva Fan Club\">Eva Fan Club</a> | <a href=\"/Evangelion_Chronicle\" title=\"Evangelion Chronicle\">Evangelion Chronicle</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><b>Production</b>: <a href=\"/Neon_Genesis_Evangelion_Proposal\" title=\"Neon Genesis Evangelion Proposal\">Neon Genesis Evangelion Proposal</a> | <a href=\"/Evangelion_Original\" title=\"Evangelion Original\">Evangelion Original</a> | <a href=\"/Neon_Genesis_Evangelion_Storyboard_Collections\" title=\"Neon Genesis Evangelion Storyboard Collections\">Storyboard Collections</a> | <a href=\"/index.php?title=Concept_Design_Collections&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Concept Design Collections (page does not exist)\">Concept Design Collections</a>\n</td></